This project is a php sqlite based simple user management system for administering users on an htdigest backend, popularly used with svn over http.  The following features are intended for the first release:


- User password reset using guid post urls (timing out)
- lite user administration
  - removing change/forgot/reg link
  - adding users, emailing them their passwords, inviting them to change it
  - initiate password reset
- email logs


features for the next release

- user initiates
  - registration
  - password change

- admin
  - auto registration
  - close registration
  - by request registration